d443a66c3a42a49e7fcbe","tid":318070,"uid":89315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有第2個玩家開咗啦<br />\n仲話集資開嘛</blockquote><br />\n個個我開錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以都係冇講？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講咩？<br />\n第二個玩家已經入左門另一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c138bf563a0be447dfb3f34c936c146cc40b9adb","tid":318070,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:05:31.000Z","msg":"門既另一邊係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893c9811964dc75dcf58c13aa6594746cd6d6542","tid":318070,"uid":4237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門既另一邊係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩都冇"},{"pid":"79b2cc21c9dba9ad707e330c386490dd9a0a5ce7","tid":318070,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同其他game唔同<br />\n尼隻game有硬值<br />\n例如唔可以同怪重疊 <br />\n同埋最重點係PVP system <br />\nPVP System先係冇得輸<br />\n追擊巴西仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尼你老母"},{"pid":"cbd51c2eb40a421c3b365c61625ad661fb930c85","tid":318070,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b599b760891cf38124e1346fc239b62c91f1886","tid":318070,"uid":43476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"好正 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11d2026eaf09b5a038f3c8c7ab6d669470bcd62","tid":318070,"uid":89315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇興趣加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}